sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente/Aplicación
    participant ProxySOAP as RollbackTaxesBulletinSoapPS
    participant ProxyREST as RollbackTaxesBulletinRestPS
    participant Pipeline as RollbackTaxesBulletinPP
    participant Template as TransferHondurasFicohsaTemplate
    participant LDAP as LDAP Security
    participant ExtractCred as ExtractCredentials.xqy
    participant TransformIn as RollbackTaxesBulletinToT24.xqy
    participant LogService as LoggingRegionalRestBS
    participant T24BS as ReversarTransaccionSoapT24BS
    participant T24 as T24 Core Banking
    participant TransformOut as T24ToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy
    participant ErrorMapper as GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS
    participant TransformError as ErrorToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy

    Note over Client, T24: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - RollbackTaxesBulletin

    alt Invocación SOAP
        Client->>ProxySOAP: SOAP Request
        Note right of Client: Endpoint: /honduras/transfer/soap/<br/>rollbackTaxesBulletin/v1<br/>Header: Basic Auth<br/>Body: rollbackTaxesBullletin
        ProxySOAP->>ProxySOAP: Validar Seguridad OWSM
        Note right of ProxySOAP: Policy: oracle/http_basic_auth_over_ssl_service_policy<br/>Validar WSS Header
        ProxySOAP->>Pipeline: Invocar Pipeline
    else Invocación REST
        Client->>ProxyREST: REST Request (JSON/XML)
        Note right of Client: Endpoint: /honduras/transfer/rest/<br/>rollbackTaxesBulletin/v1<br/>Header: Basic Auth<br/>Body: rollbackTaxesBullletin
        ProxyREST->>ProxyREST: Validar Seguridad OWSM
        Note right of ProxyREST: Policy: oracle/http_basic_auth_over_ssl_service_policy<br/>Validar WSS Header
        ProxyREST->>Pipeline: Invocar Pipeline
    end

    Pipeline->>Template: Ejecutar Template
    Note right of Pipeline: Template: TransferHondurasFicohsaTemplate.ptx

    Template->>Template: StageAssigment
    Note right of Template: Asignar variables:<br/>service='Transfer/RollbackTaxesBulletin'<br/>version='v1'<br/>key='TransactionId'<br/>value=TransactionId del body<br/>method='SOAP'<br/>operationTargetSystem='Reversionpagorecaudorefdbcta'<br/>targetSystem='T24'<br/>security='Y'<br/>originalBody=$body<br/>user=ApplicationId del body

    Template->>Template: PlaceholderID GetSecurity
    Note right of Template: Placeholder para seguridad

    Template->>Pipeline: StageSecurity
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Crear userName XML
    Note right of Pipeline: <userLoginElement><br/>  <userLogin>{ApplicationId}</userLogin><br/></userLoginElement>

    Pipeline->>ExtractCred: Invocar ExtractCredentials
    Note right of Pipeline: Parámetro: userName XML

    ExtractCred->>LDAP: lookupBasicCredentials
    Note right of ExtractCred: Path: SB_Security/Common/{ApplicationId en mayúsculas}<br/>Ejemplo: SB_Security/Common/MOBILE_BANKING

    alt Credenciales encontradas en LDAP
        LDAP-->>ExtractCred: username y password
        ExtractCred-->>Pipeline: connInfoElement con credenciales
    else Credenciales no encontradas
        LDAP-->>ExtractCred: null
        ExtractCred-->>Pipeline: connInfoElement con ApplicationId como failover
        Note left of ExtractCred: Failover: usa ApplicationId<br/>como username y password
    end

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Almacenar responseUserLogin

    Template->>Pipeline: PlaceholderID TransformRegionalToTargetSystem
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: StageTransformRequest

    Pipeline->>TransformIn: Invocar RollbackTaxesBulletinToT24.xqy
    Note right of Pipeline: Parámetros:<br/>input=$body/rollbackTaxesBullletin<br/>userConnInfo=$responseUserLogin

    TransformIn->>TransformIn: Mapear campos
    Note right of TransformIn: TransactionId → transactionId<br/>username → userName<br/>password → password<br/>company → "" (vacío)

    TransformIn-->>Pipeline: requestService (formato T24)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Almacenar requestService

    Template->>Template: StageLoggingInput
    Template->>Template: Copiar requestService a requestServiceOri

    alt security = 'Y'
        Template->>Template: Ocultar requestServiceOri
        Note right of Template: requestServiceOri = ''<br/>(por seguridad)
    end

    Template->>LogService: Invocar SaveLogInFileSystem
    Note right of Template: Registrar REQUEST:<br/>GlobalId, service, version,<br/>targetSystem, endpoint,<br/>body (oculto si security='Y')
    LogService-->>Template: Log guardado

    Template->>Pipeline: PlaceholderID InvokeCountry
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: StageInvokeCoreBanking

    Pipeline->>T24BS: wsCallout rollbackTaxesBulletin
    Note right of Pipeline: Service: ReversarTransaccionSoapT24BS<br/>Operation: rollbackTaxesBulletin<br/>Body: requestService

    T24BS->>T24: SOAP Request
    Note right of T24BS: URL: http://172.23.13.19:7003/<br/>RollbackTaxesBulletin/services<br/>Port: T24WebServicesImplPort<br/>Namespace: T24WebServicesImpl<br/>Timeout: 0 (sin límite)<br/>Retry: 0

    alt Transacción encontrada y reversada
        T24-->>T24BS: rollbackTaxesBulletinResponse
        Note left of T24: Status/successIndicator='Success'<br/>Status/messages='Transaction reversed successfully'<br/>FUNDSTRANSFERType con datos
        T24BS-->>Pipeline: responseService
        
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extraer statusService
        Note right of Pipeline: statusService = $responseService/Status/successIndicator

        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extraer codeErrorService
        Note right of Pipeline: codeErrorService = $responseService/Status/successIndicator

        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extraer messageErrorService
        Note right of Pipeline: messageErrorService = $responseService/Status/messages

    else Transacción no encontrada o error
        T24-->>T24BS: rollbackTaxesBulletinResponse
        Note left of T24: Status/successIndicator='T24Error'<br/>Status/messages='Transaction not found'
        T24BS-->>Pipeline: responseService
        
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extraer statusService
        Note right of Pipeline: statusService = 'T24Error'

        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extraer codeErrorService
        Note right of Pipeline: codeErrorService = 'T24Error'

        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extraer messageErrorService
        Note right of Pipeline: messageErrorService = 'Transaction not found'

    else Error de conexión o timeout
        T24BS-->>Pipeline: Fault
        Note left of T24BS: Error de transporte,<br/>timeout o conexión
        Pipeline->>Template: Propagar fault
        Template->>Template: Error Handler activado
        Note right of Template: Capturado por error-N53e8b9dc...
    end

    Template->>Template: StageLoggingOutput
    Template->>LogService: Invocar SaveLogInFileSystem
    Note right of Template: Registrar RESPONSE:<br/>GlobalId, statusService,<br/>codeErrorService, messageErrorService,<br/>responseService
    LogService-->>Template: Log guardado

    Template->>Pipeline: PlaceholderID TransformTargetSystemToRegional
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: StageTargetSystemToRegional

    alt codeErrorService = 'Success'
        Pipeline->>TransformOut: Invocar T24ToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy
        Note right of Pipeline: Parámetros:<br/>coreResponse=$responseService<br/>globalId=GlobalId del originalBody

        TransformOut->>TransformOut: Mapear respuesta exitosa
        Note right of TransformOut: Status=successIndicator<br/>ValueDate=substring(current-dateTime,0,11)<br/>DateTime=substring(current-dateTime,0,20)<br/>GlobalId=globalId parámetro

        TransformOut-->>Pipeline: rollbackTaxesBullletinResponse
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Reemplazar body con respuesta

    else codeErrorService != 'Success'
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Construir requestError
        Note right of Pipeline: ServicesToError.xqy:<br/>systemApplication='T24'<br/>service='Transfer/RollbackTaxesBulletin'<br/>errorMessage=$messageErrorService<br/>errorCode=$codeErrorService<br/>language=Language del originalBody

        Pipeline->>ErrorMapper: wsCallout GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS
        Note right of Pipeline: Operation: process<br/>Body: requestError
        ErrorMapper-->>Pipeline: responseError
        Note left of ErrorMapper: Retorna:<br/>code (código mapeado)<br/>error (tipo error)<br/>description (descripción completa)<br/>shortDescription (descripción corta)

        Pipeline->>TransformError: Invocar ErrorToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy
        Note right of Pipeline: Parámetros:<br/>responseError=$responseError<br/>globalId=GlobalId del originalBody<br/>codeError=$codeErrorService<br/>messageError=$messageErrorService<br/>targetSystem='T24'<br/>status=$statusService

        TransformError->>TransformError: Mapear respuesta de error
        Note right of TransformError: StatusInfo/Status=$status<br/>StatusInfo/TransactionId=''<br/>ErrorInfo/Code=$responseError/code<br/>ErrorInfo/Error=$responseError/error<br/>ErrorInfo/Description=$responseError/description<br/>ErrorInfo/Details/SystemId='T24'<br/>ErrorInfo/Details/Messages=$messageError

        TransformError-->>Pipeline: rollbackTaxesBullletinResponse con error
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Reemplazar body con respuesta error
    end

    Pipeline-->>Template: Respuesta construida
    Template-->>ProxySOAP: Respuesta
    ProxySOAP-->>Client: SOAP Response

    Note over Client, T24: Flujo de Error Handler (si ocurre excepción)

    rect rgb(255, 200, 200)
        Note over Template: Error Handler Pipeline
        Template->>Template: StageIT
        Template->>Template: Report error (logs)
        Note right of Template: Registrar:<br/>code=$fault/errorCode<br/>reason=$fault/reason<br/>uuid=GlobalId

        Template->>Template: StageMappingErrors
        Template->>Template: Construir requestError
        Note right of Template: ServicesToError.xqy:<br/>systemApplication='Vision+'<br/>service=$service<br/>errorMessage=$fault/reason<br/>errorCode=$fault/errorCode<br/>language=Language del body

        Template->>ErrorMapper: wsCallout GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS
        ErrorMapper-->>Template: responseError

        Template->>Pipeline: PlaceholderID TransformResponse
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: ErrorToRespuesta
        Pipeline->>TransformError: Invocar ErrorToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy
        Note right of Pipeline: Parámetros:<br/>responseError=$responseError<br/>globalId=GlobalId del originalBody<br/>codeError=$fault/errorCode<br/>messageError=$fault/reason<br/>targetSystem='T24'<br/>status='Error'

        TransformError-->>Pipeline: rollbackTaxesBullletinResponse con error
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Reemplazar body

        Template->>Template: StageLoggingOutputError
        Template->>LogService: Invocar SaveLogInFileSystem
        Note right of Template: Registrar ERROR:<br/>errorFlowName=$fault/location/stage<br/>codeError=$fault/errorCode<br/>messageError=$fault/reason<br/>state='Error'<br/>errorDetails=serialize($fault)
        LogService-->>Template: Log guardado

        Template->>Template: StageRespuesta
        Template->>Client: Reply con error
    end

    Note over Client, T24: Transformaciones Clave
    Note over Client, T24: 1. Extracción credenciales: LDAP lookup con failover
    Note over Client, T24: 2. Mapeo entrada: TransactionId + credenciales → T24
    Note over Client, T24: 3. Evaluación éxito: codeErrorService = 'Success'
    Note over Client, T24: 4. Mapeo salida exitosa: successIndicator + fechas generadas
    Note over Client, T24: 5. Mapeo error: Traducción códigos T24 → códigos regionales
    Note over Client, T24: 6. Logging condicional: Oculta request si security='Y'
    Note over Client, T24: 7. Preservación GlobalId: Trazabilidad end-to-end
